<fieldset><legend><h2>
        <a href="/us/">Trending in the United States</a>
        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 10 Nov 2024 17:16:22 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 10 Nov 2024 17:16:22 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="LOLITA C. BALDOR, Associated Press, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/us/2024/11/10/the-armys-answer-to-a-lack-of-recruits-is-a-prep-course-to-boost-low-scores-its-working.webp" alt="The Army's answer to a lack of recruits is a prep course to boost low scores. It's working" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">The Army's answer to a lack of recruits is a prep course to boost low scores. It's working</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      FORT JACKSON, S.C. (AP) — Index cards taped to a large board on the wall at Fort Jackson, South Carolina, reveal the sometimes blunt and gritty reasons that new recruits took a chance at a last-ditch program to get into the Army. “Eviction notices motivate me,” one said.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/11/10/the-armys-answer-to-a-lack-of-recruits-is-a-prep-course-to-boost-low-scores-its-working/"  >(LOLITA C. BALDOR, Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 09 Nov 2024 22:39:59 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 09 Nov 2024 22:39:59 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Rich Johnson, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/us/2024/11/09/militia-convicted-border-patrol-agents.webp" alt="Jury convicts two men accused of plotting to kill Border Patrol agents" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Jury convicts two men accused of plotting to kill Border Patrol agents</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Prosecutors said the men believed that  Border Patrol were committing treason by allowing immigrants to enter the country.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/11/09/militia-convicted-border-patrol-agents/"  >(Rich Johnson, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 09 Nov 2024 21:48:38 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 09 Nov 2024 21:48:38 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/us/2024/11/09/fema-worker-fired-after-directing-workers-to-avoid-helping-hurricane-survivors-who-supported-trump.webp" alt="FEMA: Worker fired after directing workers to avoid helping hurricane survivors who supported Trump" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">FEMA: Worker fired after directing workers to avoid helping hurricane survivors who supported Trump</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A Federal Emergency Management Agency worker has been fired after she directed workers helping hurricane survivors not to go to homes with yard signs supporting President-elect Donald Trump, the agency's leader said in a statement Saturday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/11/09/fema-worker-fired-after-directing-workers-to-avoid-helping-hurricane-survivors-who-supported-trump/"  >(Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 09 Nov 2024 14:45:59 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 09 Nov 2024 14:45:59 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="JAMES ELLINGWORTH, Associated Press, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/us/2024/11/09/germanys-legion-of-nfl-fans-welcomes-the-2-7-giants-and-panthers-after-brady-and-mahomes.webp" alt="Germany's legion of NFL fans welcomes the 2-7 Giants and Panthers after Brady and Mahomes" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Germany's legion of NFL fans welcomes the 2-7 Giants and Panthers after Brady and Mahomes</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      om Brady gave Germany its first taste of the NFL in 2022. Patrick Mahomes put on a show there last year.

This Sunday, Germany gets the Carolina Panthers and New York Giants, both with 2-7 records and short of star power. However, there's still an NFL buzz around Munich.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/11/09/germanys-legion-of-nfl-fans-welcomes-the-2-7-giants-and-panthers-after-brady-and-mahomes/"  >(JAMES ELLINGWORTH, Associated Press, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 06 Nov 2024 15:33:32 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 06 Nov 2024 15:33:32 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, WGN 9">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/us/2024/11/06/donald-trump-has-sweeping-plans-what-hes-proposed.webp" alt="Donald Trump has sweeping plans: What he's proposed" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Donald Trump has sweeping plans: What he's proposed</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The former president and now president-elect often skipped over details but through more than a year of policy pronouncements and written statements outlined a wide-ranging agenda that blends traditional conservative approaches to taxes, regulation and cultural issues with a more populist bent on tr
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/11/06/donald-trump-has-sweeping-plans-what-hes-proposed/"  >(The Associated Press, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 06 Nov 2024 23:47:13 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 06 Nov 2024 23:47:13 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/us/2024/11/06/mississippi-mayor-says-he-faces-political-prosecution-with-bribery-charges.webp" alt="Mississippi mayor says he faces political prosecution with bribery charges" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Mississippi mayor says he faces political prosecution with bribery charges</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      JACKSON, Miss. (AP) — The mayor of Mississippi's capital city said Wednesday that he has been indicted in an alleged bribery operation, and he said it is a “political prosecution” to hurt his 2025 campaign for reelection.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/11/06/mississippi-mayor-says-he-faces-political-prosecution-with-bribery-charges/"  >(Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 07 Nov 2024 16:08:36 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 07 Nov 2024 16:08:36 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Philip Marcelo, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/us/2024/11/07/influencer-banned-for-life-from-nyc-marathon-for-obstructing-runners-with-e-bikes-camera-person.webp" alt="Influencer banned for life from NYC Marathon for 'obstructing' runners with e-bikes, camera person" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Influencer banned for life from NYC Marathon for 'obstructing' runners with e-bikes, camera person</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      New York Road Runners, which organizes the venerable race, said in a statement Tuesday that Matthew Choi violated the group’s code of conduct and competition rules.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/11/07/influencer-banned-for-life-from-nyc-marathon-for-obstructing-runners-with-e-bikes-camera-person/"  >(Philip Marcelo, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
        <a href="/world/">Around the world</a>
        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:21:11 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:21:11 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/world/2024/11/06/china-officially-doesnt-care-about-trump-win-unofficially-experts-say-beijing-rattled.webp" alt="China officially 'doesn't care' about Trump win; unofficially, experts say Beijing is rattled" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">China officially 'doesn't care' about Trump win; unofficially, experts say Beijing is rattled</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      China&apos;s initial response to President-elect Trump&apos;s victory was matter of fact, but experts say Xi Jinping will be closely watching Trump&apos;s words and actions.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/11/06/china-officially-doesnt-care-about-trump-win-unofficially-experts-say-beijing-rattled/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 10 Nov 2024 11:38:21 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 10 Nov 2024 11:38:21 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/world/2024/11/10/un-nuclear-head-to-visit-iran-for-talks-on-countrys-nuclear-program-as-next-trump-presidency-looms.webp" alt="UN nuclear head to visit Iran for talks on country's nuclear program as next Trump presidency looms" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">UN nuclear head to visit Iran for talks on country's nuclear program as next Trump presidency looms</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      VIENNA (AP) — The head of the United Nations’ nuclear watchdog said Sunday he will travel to Iran in the coming days to hold talks regarding the country's nuclear program. The visit comes amid wider tensions gripping the Mideast over the Israel-Hamas war and uncertainty over how U.S.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/11/10/un-nuclear-head-to-visit-iran-for-talks-on-countrys-nuclear-program-as-next-trump-presidency-looms/"  >(Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 07 Nov 2024 18:26:04 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 07 Nov 2024 18:26:04 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Joe Khalil, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/world/2024/11/07/judge-revives-9-11-plea-deals.webp" alt="US military judge revives 9/11 plea deals" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">US military judge revives 9/11 plea deals</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The plea agreements would spare Mohammed, Walid bin Attash and Mustafa al-Hawsawi the risk of the death penalty.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/11/07/judge-revives-9-11-plea-deals/"  >(Joe Khalil, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 10 Nov 2024 13:40:10 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 10 Nov 2024 13:40:10 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="JON GAMBRELL, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/world/2024/11/10/soldier-with-yemens-exiled-government-opens-fire-killing-2-saudi-troops-and-wounding-another.webp" alt="Soldier with Yemen's exiled government opens fire, killing 2 Saudi troops and wounding another" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Soldier with Yemen's exiled government opens fire, killing 2 Saudi troops and wounding another</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      DUBAI, United Arab Emirates (AP) — A soldier for Yemen’s exiled government opened fire on Saudi troops as they exercised in eastern Yemen, killing two of them and wounding another in a rare insider attack during the kingdom's nearly decadelong war there, officials said Saturday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/11/10/soldier-with-yemens-exiled-government-opens-fire-killing-2-saudi-troops-and-wounding-another/"  >(JON GAMBRELL, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 10 Nov 2024 10:49:38 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 10 Nov 2024 10:49:38 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/world/2024/11/10/the-taliban-will-attend-a-un-climate-conference-for-the-1st-time.webp" alt="The Taliban will attend a UN climate conference for the 1st time" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">The Taliban will attend a UN climate conference for the 1st time</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      KABUL, Afghanistan (AP) — The Taliban will attend a U.N. climate conference for the first time since their takeover of Afghanistan in 2021, the country's national environment agency said Sunday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/11/10/the-taliban-will-attend-a-un-climate-conference-for-the-1st-time/"  >(Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 07 Nov 2024 20:57:45 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 07 Nov 2024 20:57:45 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/world/2024/11/07/australia-announces-plan-ban-social-media-kids-16.webp" alt="Australia announces plan to ban social media for kids under 16" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Australia announces plan to ban social media for kids under 16</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Australian government on Thursday announced on Thursday its intent to ban social media usage for children under 16 and hold platforms responsible for compliance.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/11/07/australia-announces-plan-ban-social-media-kids-16/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 07 Nov 2024 20:56:42 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 07 Nov 2024 20:56:42 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/world/2024/11/07/british-doctor-jailed-trying-kill-mothers-partner-fake-covid-jab.webp" alt="British doctor jailed for trying to kill mother's partner with fake COVID jab" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">British doctor jailed for trying to kill mother's partner with fake COVID jab</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Thomas Kwan, a 53-year-old British doctor, has been jailed for over 31 years for an unsuccessful plot to use a fake COVID-19 vaccine to kill his mother&apos;s partner.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/11/07/british-doctor-jailed-trying-kill-mothers-partner-fake-covid-jab/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
