    <h3 itemprop="headline">Former Bears offensive coordinator Luke Getsy fired by Raiders from same position after 9 games</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      HENDERSON, Nev. (AP) — The Bears fired Luke Getsy as their offensive coordinator right after the 2023 season ended. It didn't take a full season for the Las Vegas Raiders to follow suit.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/11/04/raiders-fire-offensive-coordinator-luke-getsy-and-2-other-offensive-coaches/"  >(MARK ANDERSON, Associated Press, WGN 9)</a>
