  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 04 Nov 2024 18:48:21 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 04 Nov 2024 18:48:21 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Bill Disbrow, WGN 9">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/politics/2024/11/04/live-emerson-college-on-final-presidential-election-swing-state-polls.webp" alt="What we learned in the final Emerson College swing state polls" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">What we learned in the final Emerson College swing state polls</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      To break down what the numbers mean, Spencer Kimball, executive director of Emerson College Polling, and a panel of Nexstar journalists from the swing states will join Chip Brewster Monday to discuss their expectations for the final vote.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/11/04/live-emerson-college-on-final-presidential-election-swing-state-polls/"  >(Bill Disbrow, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 04 Nov 2024 15:36:26 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 04 Nov 2024 15:36:26 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Caroline Bleakley, KLAS, CBS News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static10/politics/2024/11/04/nevada-offers-same-day-voter-registration.webp" alt="Not registered yet? Nevada offers same-day voter registration" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Not registered yet? Nevada offers same-day voter registration</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Same-day voter registration is available in Nevada for those with a valid Nevada driver's license or ID card, and provisional ballots are available for those whose eligibility is not yet verified.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/11/04/nevada-offers-same-day-voter-registration/"  >(Caroline Bleakley, KLAS, CBS News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset></main>
